item.title: Introducing KPI Comparisons: Gain Deeper Insights from Your Dashboards
item.description: We’re excited to announce a new feature that will help you gain more value from your KPI dashboard tiles - KPI comparisons. With KPI comparisons, you can now display the difference between your current KPI value and a different value of interest from the same table. This could be vs. the previous wave, the last year, a key competitor - whichever comparison provides the most meaningful context. For example, your brand awareness may be 73%, which seems okay on its own.
